Her repairs & recharging coming along smoothly. "Unfortunately, no. This is 
not like her to not be around me." Somewhat concerned now. Despite she herself 
was in terrible shape. 

"Perhaps," looking at the clone, "a search party should be sent out. I would 
contact Blackstorm, but my comm system is down." she hissed & winced in 'pain' 
during a moment of repair issues.
